# S01-T01: Scaffold

## Objective
Create the Vite + React + TypeScript project at `/Users/denistka/Projects/musecool`,
install all dependencies, and establish the `src/` folder structure.

## Acceptance Criteria
- `npm run dev` starts without errors.
- `src/` has: `components/`, `hooks/`, `lib/`, `game/`, `screens/`, `piano/`, `pwa/`.
- Nunito font linked in `index.html`.
- All required packages installed.

## Steps
1. `npm create vite@latest musecool -- --template react-ts` at `/Users/denistka/Projects/`.
2. Install runtime deps: `gsap tone vexflow`.
3. Install dev deps: `tailwindcss postcss autoprefixer vite-plugin-pwa`.
4. Create folder structure under `src/`.
5. Add Google Fonts link for Nunito (600,700,800,900) to `index.html`.
6. Replace Vite boilerplate: clear `App.tsx`, `App.css`; keep `main.tsx` + `index.css`.
7. Add `"paths": { "@/*": ["./src/*"] }` alias to `tsconfig.json` + `vite.config.ts`.
8. `git init && git remote add origin https://github.com/denistka/musecool.git`.
9. `git add . && git commit -m "chore: scaffold" && git push -u origin main`.
